anns.task_desc: rinse the mug from the coffee machine and put it back

high_descs: Walk towards the window, then hang a left and walk up to the counter.
Pick up the dirty coffee mug that is in the coffee machine on the counter.
Walk over to the sink behind you.
Wash the dirty mug in the sink and then pick it back up.
Turn around and walk over to the counter.
Put the clean mug in the coffee machine on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean mug in the coffee machine.

high_descs: Go across the room to the coffee maker.
Pick up the mug on the coffee maker.
Turn around and go to the sink.
Rinse off the mug in the right side of the sink and pick it back up.
Turn around and go back to the coffee maker.
Put the mug on the coffee maker.
anns.task_desc: Put a rinsed mug on the coffee maker.
